For my project I plan to look at the stats of Colin Kaepernick and compare him to Quarterbacks who are still in the league to show that his blacklisting from the league is not about stats. I will compare the average amount of yards gained on the play,

Thesis: From the data collected and graphs presented Colin Kaepernick stats from his 2015 season with the San Francisco 49ers places Kaepernick as an above average quarterback, compared to quarterbacks who have over 300 passes.
